The paper proposes a method to modify traditional CNNs to make them interpretable, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The method involves assigning each filter in a high conv-layer with an object part during the learning process, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the clear knowledge representation in an interpretable CNN, which is a topic related to neural networks (cs.NE) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
